@startuml security-secrets-flow
title Управление секретами (HashiCorp Vault) — Enterprise ML Platform (Baseline/Alpha)

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 5
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

participant "K8s API Server" as K8s
participant "Pod\n(vault-agent-init\nsidecar)" as VaultAgent
participant "Vault\n(HA, 3 replicas)" as Vault
database "PostgreSQL" as PG
participant "Application\nContainer" as App
participant "cert-manager" as CertMgr

== Pod Startup: получение секретов ==

note over K8s, App
  Vault Agent Sidecar Pattern:
  сервисы не содержат логики работы с Vault.
  Секреты инжектируются как файлы.
end note

K8s -> VaultAgent : Pod scheduled\n(initContainer: vault-agent-init)
VaultAgent -> Vault : POST /v1/auth/kubernetes/login\n{jwt: ServiceAccount JWT, role: "model-service"}
note right of Vault
  K8s Auth: Vault проверяет JWT
  через K8s TokenReview API.
  Каждый сервис — отдельная роль
  с минимальными правами (least privilege).
end note
Vault --> VaultAgent : {client_token, lease_id, lease_duration=1h}

VaultAgent -> Vault : GET /v1/database/creds/model-service-role
Vault -> PG : CREATE ROLE vault_model_svc_abc\nGRANT SELECT, INSERT ON models, model_versions
PG --> Vault : role created
Vault --> VaultAgent : {username: "vault_model_svc_abc",\npassword: "<random>", lease_ttl=3600s}

VaultAgent -> VaultAgent : Write /vault/secrets/db-creds\n{username, password}
note right of VaultAgent
  Файл доступен только приложению
  (tmpfs mount, chmod 0400).
end note

VaultAgent -> K8s : initContainer Done
K8s -> App : Container started\n(/vault/secrets/ volume mounted)
App -> App : Read /vault/secrets/db-creds\n(inotify watch for updates)

== Автоматическая ротация (zero-downtime) ==

note over VaultAgent, PG
  Two-key overlap window: Vault создаёт новый credential
  за 30% до истечения TTL. Старый credential работает
  до завершения in-flight запросов (grace period 60s).
end note

VaultAgent -> Vault : Renew lease (TTL - 30%)
alt Lease renewable
    Vault --> VaultAgent : {new_lease_duration=3600s}
else Lease max TTL exceeded → rotate
    Vault -> PG : CREATE ROLE vault_model_svc_xyz\nDROP ROLE vault_model_svc_abc (after grace)
    PG --> Vault : rotated
    Vault --> VaultAgent : {new username, new password}
    VaultAgent -> VaultAgent : Update /vault/secrets/db-creds
    App -> App : inotify → reload DB connection pool\n(graceful: drain existing connections)
end

== TLS-сертификаты (cert-manager) ==

CertMgr -> Vault : POST /v1/pki/issue/mlplatform\n{common_name: "model-service.ml-platform.svc"}
Vault --> CertMgr : {certificate, private_key,\nca_chain, expiry=90d}
CertMgr -> K8s : Create/Update Secret\n(type: kubernetes.io/tls)
note right of CertMgr
  Автоматический renewal за 30 дней
  до истечения (NFR-403).
  При сбое автоматики — ручной
  renewal через cert-manager CLI.
end note

== Типы секретов в Vault ==

note over Vault
  KV v2:    API-ключи платформы → secret/mlplatform/api-keys/
  Dynamic:  PostgreSQL creds → database/creds/{role}
  AWS:      S3/IAM creds → aws/creds/{role} (или IRSA preferred)
  PKI:      TLS certs → pki/issue/{role}
  Transit:  Envelope encryption → transit/encrypt/mlplatform-key
            (используется для SSE-KMS артефактов моделей)
end note

@enduml
